  "description": [
    "SIX Goodman Band Concert Set For Nav\u00dfase A concert featuring Benny Goodman and his Orchestra will be presented on the Naval Base Bldg 1801 on 8 Sept at 2100 Goodman and his band have just recently returned from a tour of Soviet Russia His ap pearances in Russia were under the auspices of the U S State Departments Cultural Exchange program While in Russia he ap peared in six cities for approx imately 200000 fans Tickets for the concert on the Naval Base may be obtained at the Special Services Office Bldg 114 or from LTJG Bruce Lewel lyn Schools Command Public In formation Officer Tickets are also available from various business places in Newport Proceeds from the concert which is sponsored by the New port Music Festival Inc will go to the Boys Clubs of Newport County Brown Wins Public Works Golf Tourney YNI Joe Brown of the Naval Station Legal Office captured first place in the ninehole Naval Base Public Works Golf League Handicap Tournament played Tuesday 14 Aug Brown took the honors with a low net of 29 w r ith a 13 stroke handicap Browns low net of 29 was closely followed by BTI Pete Blitchington"
